{"tid":36343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視與相關公司被追貨款逾百萬","createTime":"2016-12-12T15:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T00:14:27.000Z","uid":17738,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d52103f1fdf80e70bf55a779b87c8b6eb2834383","tid":36343,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"樂視與相關公司被追貨款逾百萬<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-12 16:52:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頻頻傳出財困的樂視繼月初遭香港經濟日報有限公司入稟追討53.5萬廣告費後，樂視及其相關公司再遭一間公司入稟，就一批電腦軟件及電子器材追討共逾105.2萬元貨款。<br />\n<br />\n原告為美高域有限公司，分別向樂視有限公司追討51.3萬元，及向樂視體育文化產業發展（香港）有限公司追討53.9萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56038004&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56038004%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161212&d=wf1j%2FBAVpNFcDbTK2ztEX2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=31ec8817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56038004%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161212&h=ed595143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56038004&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161212</a>"},{"pid":"3a9b8757bd4caae88528da3f376312162ef60856","tid":36343,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"終於收皮？"},{"pid":"a4f4e2603117902e0e7ceff167f076b50b32ca93","tid":36343,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於收皮？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n差無幾，上次又話白武士注資6億美元原來係吹嘅"},{"pid":"e0a28f29b937c63613e0d75a76451fc945e4b64f","tid":36343,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"支爆先兆 ?"},{"pid":"606430270fc8e3c6ba9dd97e36b0c08bdfc58188","tid":36343,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB